| `src/application/turn.rs` | The top-level turn loop already performs interpretation, initial action selection, recursive loop dispatch, synthesis/finalization, and thread decision handling. Error text still says "Runtime lanes not initialized." | Preserve as canonical center; rename runtime initialization around prepared turn runtime. |
| `src/application/agent_loop.rs` | Drives recursive planner loop: action selection, governance, retrieval, tool execution, evidence accumulation, refinement, replan, and stop/direct answer decisions. | Preserve as turn-loop action/execution phase, not a separate public planner lane. |
